OL,3,CJune heatwave keeps shoppers away from
OL,4,Cthe high street in blow to retailers
OL,6,FJune's record heatwave brought a blow
OL,7,Fto retailers as the uncomfortable
OL,8,Ftemperatures kept shoppers away from
OL,9,Fthe high street, figures show.
OL,11,FTotal UK footfall was down 3.4% year
OL,12,Fon year last month, with the high
OL,13,Fstreet suffering the sharpest 6.2%
OL,14,Fdecline in shopper numbers, according
OL,15,Fto British Retail Consortium (BRC)-
OL,16,FSensormatic data.
OL,18,FAir-conditioned shopping centres and
OL,19,Fretail parks proved more resilient,
OL,20,Fwith visitors down 2.5% and 0.3%
OL,21,Frespectively on last June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
