OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783648071
OL,3,CJune heatwave keeps shoppers away from
OL,4,Cthe high street in blow to retailers
OL,6,FScotland was the only nation to
OL,7,Fexperience a rise in overall footfall,
OL,8,Fup 1.7%, with Northern Ireland, Wales
OL,9,Fand England seeing declines of 0.9%,
OL,10,F2.3% and 3% respectively.
OL,12,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,13,Fsaid: "The heatwave may have affected
OL,14,Ffootfall, but retailers face a bigger
OL,15,Fchallenge: rising costs.
OL,17,F"Businesses are working hard to
OL,18,Fdeliver value for customers, yet
OL,19,Fhigher taxes and regulatory burdens
OL,20,Fare making it harder to invest, create
OL,21,Fjobs and grow.
OL,26,@uD@GOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
