OL,3,CJune heatwave keeps shoppers away from
OL,4,Cthe high street in blow to retailers
OL,6,F"Exceptionally high temperatures are
OL,7,Flikely to have influenced behaviour,
OL,8,Fparticularly in the South, where
OL,9,Frecord heat and travel disruption made
OL,10,Fshopping trips less appealing.
OL,12,F"At the same time, consumer confidence
OL,13,Fis improving slightly but remains low,
OL,14,Fwith wider uncertainty continuing to
OL,15,Fweigh on discretionary spend."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@^O]
